OL,3,CConcerns over costs to deliver
OL,4,CJersey's new hospital, report finds
OL,6,FUnderstated revenue costs, unclear
OL,7,Fstaffing plans, and a lack of overall
OL,8,Fstrategy are just some key findings of
OL,9,Fa damning report into Jersey's plans
OL,10,Fto overhaul the island's health
OL,11,Ffacilities.
OL,13,FJersey's Hospital Review Panel -
OL,14,Fchaired by Deputy Jonathan Renouf -
OL,15,Freleased a 117-page review of the
OL,16,FGovernment's New Healthcare Facilities
OL,17,FProgramme.
