OL,3,CConcerns over costs to deliver
OL,4,CJersey's new hospital, report finds
OL,6,FThe report states: "There is a clear
OL,7,Frisk that the future revenue costs of
OL,8,Fthe four facilities (...) cannot be
OL,9,Ffunded within the identified future
OL,10,Fbudget and that additional funding
OL,11,Fwill have to be found or savings will
OL,12,Fhave to be made."
OL,14,FIt also highlighted a lack of detail
OL,15,Fregarding workforce and operational
OL,16,Fcost projects and revenue forecasts
OL,17,Fnot accounting for inflation.
OL,19,FHowever, Jersey's Health Minister
OL,20,Fclaims the report "is likely to cause
OL,21,Fa good deal of unnecessary concern".
