OL,3,CConcerns over costs to deliver
OL,4,CJersey's new hospital, report finds
OL,6,FChair of the Hospital Review Panel,
OL,7,FDeputy Jonathan Renouf says the main
OL,8,Fconcern is the lack of detail on the
OL,9,FOverdale site.
OL,11,FIn particular to Overdale, key details
OL,12,Fincluding how large the hospital will
OL,13,Fbe, what treatments it will provide,
OL,14,Fand how it will meet the island's
OL,15,Fneeds are omitted.
OL,17,FDeputy Renouf explains: "Basically in
OL,18,F(the UK advisors') view, it did not
OL,19,Fmeet the standard that they would
OL,20,Fexpect to see for a capital project of
OL,21,Fthis scale and importance.
