OL,3,CConcerns over costs to deliver
OL,4,CJersey's new hospital, report finds
OL,6,F"We don't have the assurance that the
OL,7,Fplans that have been put forward will
OL,8,Fmeet the healthcare needs of the
OL,9,Fisland first of all and secondly
OL,10,Fwhether that's affordable in terms of
OL,11,Fbuilding them or in terms of running
OL,12,Fthem further down the line."
OL,14,FDeparate to Overdale, the report also
OL,15,Findicated the risk that the new
OL,16,Ffacilities will not be delivered in
OL,17,Ftime for the multi-site model to be
OL,18,Fimplemented.
