OL,3,CConcerns over costs to deliver
OL,4,CJersey's new hospital, report finds
OL,6,FDeputy Renouf raised concerns that
OL,7,Fmoney might be pulled from those
OL,8,Ffacilities to focus on Overdale.
OL,10,FHe adds: "The risk is in order to stay
OL,11,Fwithin the financial envelope, they
OL,12,Fmight put less into the hospital and
OL,13,Fhave a lesser standard of quality. We
OL,14,Fmight turn out fine, but the
OL,15,Finformation just isn't there for us to
OL,16,Ftell.
