OL,3,CConcerns over costs to deliver
OL,4,CJersey's new hospital, report finds
OL,6,F"This is the biggest single capital
OL,7,Fproject the island's government will
OL,8,Fever probably undertake so getting it
OL,9,Fright really matters, particularly in
OL,10,Fterms of affordability going forward.
OL,12,F"The consequences of getting this
OL,13,Fwrong will ripple on for generations."
OL,15,FIn a statement responding to the
OL,16,Fpanel's report, Health Minister,
OL,17,FDeputy Tom Binet, says he will
OL,18,Fcarefully study its findings but
OL,19,Fremains confident with plans.
